text: The Phou Samsoum tree frog (Zhangixalus melanoleucus) is a frog. It lives in Laos in Xiengkhouang Province. People have only seen it in one place: Phou Samsoum Mountain. Scientists think it might also live in other mountainous parts of Laos and Vietnam. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia
title: Zhangixalus melanoleucus
